<li> <a href="http://releases.ubuntu.com/releases/6.06/">Ubuntu 6.06.2 LTS (Dapper Drake)</a> ------ 192MB</li>
<li> <a href="http://releases.ubuntu.com/releases/7.04/">Ubuntu 7.04 (Feisty Fawn)</a> ------ 256MB</li>
<li> <a href="http://releases.ubuntu.com/releases/7.10/">Ubuntu 7.10 (Gutsy Gibbon)</a> ------ 320MB</li>
<li> <a href="http://releases.ubuntu.com/releases/8.04/">Ubuntu 8.04 LTS (Hardy Heron) Beta</a> ------ 384MB</li>
</ol>
可怜我的一台老机器只有320MB的内存，就停留在了Ubuntu 6.06上。"
